text: Adaeze Ifeyinwa Ossai is a Nigerian Civil service, philanthropist and founder of Merry Readers Club. She is known on her contribution for female education. Adaeze is a native of Udenu Local government area (LGA), Enugu State. ==References== Category:Missing births Category:Living people Category:People from Enugu State
